name: GSL
info: Welcome to the GSL! The premier league of Starcraft 2 which tests the skills of all comers to see if they are worthy of a championship title! The GSL is a stage where the highest levels of production and gaming skills come together to provide a global standard for eSports broadcast.

info: JaeWon 'Crank' Choi is a full time South Korean streamer. A veteran of the StarCraft eSports scene for 10 years, CranK plays StarCraft 2 and a variety of other games.
